data.description: This dreamy coastal cottage awaits in the Palm Cove community, just a short distance to the beautiful sands of Panama City Beach.  A turn-key investment property with proven rental numbers or a welcoming primary residence, step inside to one-level living, tasteful decor, and cozy furnishings throughout. Your new home will make for the best memories in one of the most affordable communities around, 2 neighborhood pools and community playground included!  Boasting 3 bedrooms/2 full bathrooms, a garage, spacious laundry room, updated kitchen, and private screened-in patio, this one truly has it all.  Located by award-winning restaurants, shopping, fitness centers, entertainment and of course-- the beach.  Your search stops here, so call your favorite agent for a showing today!
